{"tid":83358,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"十年快過去，唔知小皮球生活是否安好？","createTime":"2017-01-16T16:08:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T06:10:10.000Z","uid":3806,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"92889256e3bec144b37fcc36927cd5284b8e9940","tid":83358,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:08:15.000Z","msg":"於2007年5月5日17時53分，即中學會考英文科聆聽考試翌日，高登會員小皮球(高乘駿9up)於高登討論區發表文章聲稱自己設置發射站干擾大氣電波，以達致影響其他考生聆聽答卷材料為目的[1]。<br />\n<br />\n此等行為被一眾高登人看成假膠、「博上位」的行為。可是，亦有不少會考生會員表示文章令人極反感，不安。亦有會員表示有報警的意圖。<br />\n<br />\n發展<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不知是湊巧還是另有原因，文章發表翌日《蘋果日報》報道，有不少元朗考生向該報投訴，指自己於應考英文科聆聽卷時收音機接收有問題。[2]<br />\n<br />\n2007年5月6日14時46分，即事情發生的翌日，高登會員細so於吹水台發表文章，於文章內附上即將寄往考評局及《蘋果日報》之電郵的圖片，並附上小皮球上報文章之連結[3]。不少會員急購花生，試圖以低買高賣以賺取膠幣圖利。<br />\n<br />\n2007年5月7日5時31分，高登會員小飛飛於吹水台發表文章，附有小皮球事件再次上報的報章內容[4][5]。此次引來大批會員急購花生及恥笑，再次令花生價位一度高漲，影響花生業的行情。文章提及考評局已報警處理事件，而小皮球方面則未曾成功聯絡上。"},{"pid":"df7a8a05b8a2558cdaa8915fee4d2162ab918a03","tid":83358,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:08:51.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】考試及評核局昨日報警，要求警方調查有網友自爆在上周六干擾元朗會考試場內考生接收電台廣播英語聆聽試一事，電訊管理局也正跟進事件。考評局表示，到昨日共接獲17名來自元朗考場考生懷疑被干擾的投訴。但事件主角──網友「小皮球」昨日隨即反口，聲言只是開玩笑，並無真正進行干擾。<br />\n<br />\n干擾者自稱「吹水」<br />\n會考英語聆聽試在上周六上午進行，網友「小皮球」當日下午在高登討論區上留言，指自己已在元朗區放置發射器，干擾考試。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一名自稱「小皮球」的男子昨主動致電本報，首先聲稱自己只是「玩」和「吹水」，該題目只是抄自其他網站，當日他其實沒有干擾考試。言談間，他要求記者不要再報道，又多次問記者這樣「吹水」是否犯法，也提及過往曾發生多宗網上留言惹官非事件。<br />\n然而，他後來又反口指自己只是「小皮球」朋友，並非事主本人。當記者再致電他時，他說「小皮球」沒有興趣回應。<br />\n「小皮球」昨在網上留言，不斷強調自己只是「吹水」，但不少網友指他「知衰」，有人揶揄說相信他的解釋，「不過你都係留番同法官講啦。」更有網友留言披露他姓高。</span><br />\n<br />\n接獲17名考生投訴<br />\n考評局發言人昨表示已就事件報警求助，至昨共接獲17名元朗考生報稱當日考試時，收音機接收受到干擾。電訊管理局指已跟進該個案，並提醒市民違例干擾電波屬刑事罪，最高可被判罰款10萬元及入獄5年。<br />\n另外，一名姓楊會考生投訴，上周六在北角閩僑中學應考英語聆聽試時，收音機除聽到試題外，也收到其他電台廣播，考試受到嚴重影響。考評局發言人表示，總共收到兩宗來自該考場的設訴，會作出跟進。"},{"pid":"1c6f758d049033b80b62a11c9943868863d48868","tid":83358,"uid":30285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:08:56.000Z","msg":"......"},{"pid":"886b9948562bb7cea815e63616cf2e6ae2721f1a","tid":83358,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:10:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>......</blockquote><br />\nfake"},{"pid":"ff562395e588af440a41455ee0e2f1a498588ad1","tid":83358,"uid":22642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:10:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>......</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb67d2ba8fe1a3e78dbb54bc22c769e5e15407d","tid":83358,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:11:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20070507/large/A08_01_a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20070507%2Flarge%2FA08_01_a.gif&h=48a12ffb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d234ff6a1f77fede2d74277efd8b27083b1a9e2d","tid":83358,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:12:50.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】<span style=\"color: red;\">元朗區會考試場懷疑發生蓄意干擾聆聽試事件。會考英語聆聽試前日舉行，該區多個試場透過電台接收試題訊號時，離奇遭受干擾。有網友於考試當日表示在試場附近擺放發射器，蓄意干擾大氣電波，目的是「送佢（考生）一程」。考評局正跟進考生對聆聽試接收不清的投訴。　記者：白琳<br />\n<br />\n會考英語聆聽試於前日早上舉行，網友「小皮球」當日下午旋即在高登討論區留言，表示自己在試場附近擺放干擾範圍500米的發射器，「今日元朗大馬路一帶考會考生，極有可能聽到不完整試題。」他無透露自己是否考生，只在討論區解釋，「元朗地方咪 band5學校多，佢都交白卷啦，不如我送佢一程仲好。」<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n每次歷時達一分鐘<br />\n本報於同日接獲劉姓會考生投訴。他昨日仍氣憤難平，表示當日在元朗天主中學應考聆聽試，以 FM96.4頻道接收試題時，多次遭受干擾，每次歷時一分鐘，「我已經帶兩部收音機，都係沙到聽唔到，隨時因為咁低一個 grade，對我好唔公平！」他有同學在附近試場也遭遇相同問題，包括元朗商會中學及元朗公立中學，應考考生逾百人。他相信有人蓄意干擾，已電郵考評局及警方投訴，要求盡快徹查事件及調整該區考生分數。<br />\n本報昨日未能聯絡「小皮球」。考評局表示，正跟進該區接收不清的個案，但難以單憑網上留言追查是否有人蓄意干擾；元朗警署暫未接獲考生報警。<br />\n立法會議員張文光表示，雖然不能排除網上留言只屬惡作劇，但考評局若發現表面證據成立，應徹底追查有無人蓄意干擾考試，並安撫受到影響的考生。</span><br />\n<br />\n屢次出現接收不清<br />\n會考及高考聆聽試早年在試場內以播放錄音帶形式進行，因器材維修保養開支龐大，於95年起改由港台廣播，但屢屢出現接收不清問題。<br />\n此外，當日在九龍華仁書院應考聆聽試的另一劉姓考生向本報投訴，指聆聽試無故提早15分鐘完結。事後監考員向他承認「搞錯」，劉同學已去信考評局投訴。考評局則指有關個案尚待查證。<br />\n<br />\n違法行為：藏干擾器材可判監<br />\n網友「小皮球」在高登討論區聲稱使用發射器干擾聆聽試，事件引起網友討論干擾方法，更有人上載自製干擾器照片。<br />\n理工大學電子及資訊工程學系高級講師周海林指技術上完全可行，成本也只需數百元。法律界人士則警告，管有相關器材已屬違法。<br />\n周海林解釋，市面有一種非法售賣的「調頻發射機」，干擾範圍約十數米，主要用來將手提 MP3機的音樂傳至車內的收音機播放。只要稍經改裝，干擾範圍即可擴至數百米。<br />\n但法律界人士鄧達明指，根據《電訊條例》第32A條，管有或使用未經授權的無線電發射器，最高可罰款50,000元及監禁2年；以往曾有無線電發燒友被控此罪，法官大多罰款了事，若今次有人惡意犯案令考生利益受損，則屬嚴重罪行，「一旦罪成，好可能要坐監!」<br />\n本報記者"},{"pid":"131d659ab082a3edc71c99bbaba53931ffd06f57","tid":83358,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:16:32.000Z","msg":"仲有白安宇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa20d70258165193f53a6d6cbb2808f48bd1ea3c","tid":83358,"uid":14872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:58:44.000Z","msg":"牙蓋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bfb6b4d55f611c1e38fcb9bbd97e4a2e064c684","tid":83358,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T18:49:45.000Z","msg":"十年又過去，蓋青仲on99"},{"pid":"840b94528a1503856032d9666d571c2066dd8e6a","tid":83358,"uid":56838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T23:02:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十年又過去，蓋青仲on99</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nJuno 嘅 念念不忘？"},{"pid":"fc847d2b276f9339968f43ab2b5604ad5aa9db74","tid":83358,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T23:48:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>牙蓋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e57356cd951f963a0bd05f01e9ae011d273cb50c","tid":83358,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T01:28:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>十年又過去，蓋青仲on99</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nJuno 嘅 念念不忘？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc889c90216d5331f1345d59889eedac4fef870","tid":83358,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T01:46:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>十年又過去，蓋青仲on99</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nJuno 嘅 念念不忘？</blockquote><br />\n幾岩音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e05618c73c50824915587c0ca79e8aec45a464de","tid":83358,"uid":3806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:11:52.000Z","msg":"蓋清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e057f04fe6df8cb4820af57f86006e5f8626d8","tid":83358,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T23:58:57.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"5b8d3154ed2a74b22c8a22d300ccfec9c581b4a6","tid":83358,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T00:04:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aff31ab51910df00d877aa972beca346cd7e1b6","tid":83358,"uid":3806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T03:41:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小皮球😄👋🏻"},{"pid":"93e8472b06eb07bf07c96064b0161bf340009ae6","tid":83358,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:11:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小皮球😄👋🏻</blockquote><br />\n唔好講以前"},{"pid":"c6750a05b41f247de75454e49ad222db0f3252ad","tid":83358,"uid":3806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T07:17:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小皮球😄👋🏻</blockquote><br />\n唔好講以前</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20070507/large/A08_01_a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20070507%2Flarge%2FA08_01_a.gif&h=48a12ffb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84646246f64ba7b15357411c267f84793af47c8b","tid":83358,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T07:19:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n小皮球😄👋🏻</blockquote><br />\n唔好講以前</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20070507/large/A08_01_a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20070507%2Flarge%2FA08_01_a.gif&h=48a12ffb&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n一場誤會"},{"pid":"07b280e0db8c4c7a20f06a05e6309523bddd8e72","tid":83358,"uid":41157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T09:56:55.000Z","msg":"話時話講馬果個高乘進都收左皮"},{"pid":"a43bb71babe98071d1b18debd584c082c026b806","tid":83358,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T06:10:10.000Z","msg":"支持"}]}